    "chapter": {
        "bookTitle": "D&C",
        "delineation": "Section",
        "number": 34,
        "summary": "1\u20134, The faithful become the sons of God through the Atonement; 5\u20139, The preaching of the gospel prepares the way for the Second Coming; 10\u201312, Prophecy comes by the power of the Holy Ghost.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
        "verses": [
            {
                "text": "My son Orson, hearken and hear and behold what I, the Lord God, shall say unto you, even Jesus Christ your Redeemer;",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 52:26; 103:40; 124:129; 136:13.",
                        "start": 7,
                        "end": 12
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "The light and the life of the world, a light which shineth in darkness and the darkness comprehendeth it not;",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "John 1:5.",
                        "start": 4,
                        "end": 9
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Who so loved the world that he gave his own life, that as many as would believe might become the sons of God. Wherefore you are my son;",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "John 3:16; 15:13. TG\u00a0Love.",
                        "start": 7,
                        "end": 12
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Jesus Christ, Redeemer.",
                        "start": 31,
                        "end": 35
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Luke 8:21; John 1:12 (9\u201313); Rom. 8:17 (12\u201317); Moses 6:68 (64\u201368). TG\u00a0Sons and Daughters of God.",
                        "start": 97,
                        "end": 101
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And blessed are you because you have believed;",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "John 20:29.",
                        "start": 4,
                        "end": 11
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And more blessed are you because you are called of me to preach my gospel\u2014",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Called of God.",
                        "start": 41,
                        "end": 47
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "To lift up your voice as with the sound of a trump, both long and loud, and cry repentance unto a crooked and perverse generation, preparing the way of the Lord for his second coming.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 24:12.",
                        "start": 45,
                        "end": 50
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 3:20; 6:9; 18:14.",
                        "start": 76,
                        "end": 79
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Matt. 3:3.",
                        "start": 131,
                        "end": 140
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Jesus Christ, Second Coming; Millennium, Preparing a People for.",
                        "start": 169,
                        "end": 182
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "For behold, verily, verily, I say unto you, the time is soon at hand that I shall come in a cloud with power and great glory.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Rev. 1:3.",
                        "start": 48,
                        "end": 52
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Jesus Christ, Prophecies about.",
                        "start": 82,
                        "end": 86
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Num. 11:25; Luke 21:27; Ether 2:4 (4\u20135, 14); JS\u2014H 1:68 (68\u201371).",
                        "start": 92,
                        "end": 97
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And it shall be a great day at the time of my coming, for all nations shall tremble.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Joel 2:11; Mal. 4:5; D&C 2:1; 43:17 (17\u201326). TG\u00a0Day of the Lord.",
                        "start": 18,
                        "end": 27
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Isa. 64:2.",
                        "start": 76,
                        "end": 83
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "But before that great day shall come, the sun shall be darkened, and the moon be turned into blood; and the stars shall refuse their shining, and some shall fall, and great destructions await the wicked.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Last Days.",
                        "start": 42,
                        "end": 45
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Wherefore, lift up your voice and spare not, for the Lord God hath spoken; therefore prophesy, and it shall be given by the power of the Holy Ghost.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Isa. 58:1.",
                        "start": 34,
                        "end": 39
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Prophets, Mission of.",
                        "start": 85,
                        "end": 93
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "2\u00a0Pet. 1:21; D&C 18:32; 42:16; 68:3.",
                        "start": 124,
                        "end": 129
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And if you are faithful, behold, I am with you until I come\u2014",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And verily, verily, I say unto you, I come quickly. I am your Lord and your Redeemer. Even so. Amen.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 33:18.",
                        "start": 43,
                        "end": 50
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Jesus Christ, Lord.",
                        "start": 62,
                        "end": 66
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            }
        ]
    }
}